data.title: German Serie D
data.text:
Issuing Company: Maple Leaf Gum

Country of Issue: Germany

Year of Issue: 1950s

Color/B&W: Color

Number of Cards in Set: 105

Card Size: 1 7/8" x 2 3/4"

Issued as insert with what product: Gum

Notes: Checklist incomplete. No company name listed. Paper thin on glossy paper. Issued in groups of 35, up to number 105.

These have text on the back in German, but can also be found with blank backs.

Date info: Serie B was issued in about 1955, so this set was probably issued fairly soon after that set.

Thanks to Ralf Wierz and Nick Bolton for help with this checklist.
